org.apache.fineract.batch.command

Class CommandContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.fineract.batch.command.CommandContext

  • public class CommandContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides an object to BatchApiService to get the proper commandStrategy for each request in BatchRequest. It uses Builder pattern to create object of this type.

    Rishabh Shukla
